<Author>Irishkisser
<Content>Good value/location Hotel very well situated for S+U bahn. If arriving at Schoenefeld airport S9 train takes you to S. Charlottenburg then 3 minute walk. Restaurants and bars all within walking distance, or again easy links to centre stations.Staff very friendly both at check in and breakfast; breakfast itself basic but good choice and always restocked.Hotel and rooms very clean; only downside was the bathroom, or should say showerroom. No bath in our room although some have them (as a group, out of 7 rooms, 2 had baths). Bear it in mind when booking if you like a soak. Other than that would recommend this hotel. 
