<Author>WaltR
<Content>A reasonable choice This hotel is very convenient for both the S bahn and U bahn transport systems being only about 2 minutes walk from both. The young staff were all very helpful and all spoke far better English than my limited German. The breakfast was adequate but a tour group sat before us ate all the bacon and despite a request for more none was forthcoming. The room was clean but if I stayed again I would ask for a room on the inside rather than one overlooking the main road as that turned out to be rather noisy if you kept the window open - there was no air conditioning. 
